edu.spa.ftclib.internal

Class Robot

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.spa.ftclib.internal.Robot
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BNO055HolonomicBot, Pushbot

    public class Robot
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Gabriel on 2017-12-29. We find it helpful to have a single "hardware robot" class with all the sensors, servos, etc. that make up a robot, so we don't have to initialize them in every op-mode. It's also helpful to include the hardwareMap and telemetry. If you're using the drivetrain part of our library, you'll also want a drivetrain. You may find it helpful to extend this class to create your own "hardware robot" class.
